    <item>
      <title>Will AI Replace Excel: Separating Fact from Fiction</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/ai-replace-excel/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:23:51 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/ai-replace-excel/</guid>
      <description>AI is not likely to replace Excel entirely, but it will significantly change how we use spreadsheets. AI-powered tools will augment human capabilities, automating repetitive tasks and enhancing data analysis.</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Unlocking AI in Excel: A Step-by-Step Guide</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/how-to-turn-on-ai-in-excel/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 08:23:51 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/how-to-turn-on-ai-in-excel/</guid>
      <description>To turn on AI in Excel, go to the &amp;lsquo;Data&amp;rsquo; tab, click on &amp;lsquo;From Other Sources&amp;rsquo;, and select &amp;lsquo;From Microsoft AI&amp;rsquo;. Alternatively, use the &amp;rsquo; Ideas&amp;rsquo; button in the &amp;lsquo;Home&amp;rsquo; tab to access AI-powered suggestions. Enable AI tools like &amp;lsquo;Text to Columns&amp;rsquo; or &amp;lsquo;Flash Fill&amp;rsquo; for data analysis and automation</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Revolutionizing Excel with AI: A Comprehensive Guide to Creating Formulas</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/using-ai-to-create-excel-formulas/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 16:23:51 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/using-ai-to-create-excel-formulas/</guid>
      <description>Yes, you can use AI to create Excel formulas, leveraging machine learning algorithms to automate and simplify your spreadsheet tasks. AI-powered tools can generate formulas, validate data, and even provide suggestions for optimization.</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Unlocking ChatGPT&#39;s Potential: Mastering Excel Formulas and Beyond</title>
      <link>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/can-chatgpt-do-excel-formulas/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 16:23:51 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/can-chatgpt-do-excel-formulas/</guid>
      <description>ChatGPT can understand and generate Excel formulas to a certain extent, but its capabilities have limitations. It can be a useful tool for simple to moderately complex formulas, but may struggle with highly complex or specialized formulas.</description>
    </item>
